    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From Farming to Merchant Competition</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey starting as a small Venetian farmer stepping into the challenging and exciting world of trade. Increase your wealth by selling your products in markets, compete with other merchants, and become a respected trader in Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193990/extras/9bb68cb06af98b0a5f0213f567e92fa3.poster.avif?t=1766576446\" width=700 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193990/extras/9bb68cb06af98b0a5f0213f567e92fa3.webm?t=1766576446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration In A Boundless Open World</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roam freely in our open world, crafted with detailed and vivid depictions of medieval Europe. Write your own adventure across this vast geography that stretches from cities to rural areas, from seas to mountains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193990/extras/8d4fd2c3045e76fc4720421c12ecc794.poster.avif?t=1766576446\" width=700 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193990/extras/8d4fd2c3045e76fc4720421c12ecc794.webm?t=1766576446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thrilling Battles On land and Sea</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to trade, engage in strategic land and sea battles. Fight aboard ships and build an army to protect your caravan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193990/extras/2ba51650b7967eb623d1b0d43d8f50c5.poster.avif?t=1766576446\" width=700 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193990/extras/2ba51650b7967eb623d1b0d43d8f50c5.webm?t=1766576446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An Enriched Gaming Experience with Extra Activities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop your character and enhance your enjoyment of the game with various activities like hunting, fishing, and farming. Use the resources nature provides to grow both your skills and your fortune.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193990/extras/cc6ea27c555a24653b99f8bfac5f06d3.poster.avif?t=1766576446\" width=700 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193990/extras/cc6ea27c555a24653b99f8bfac5f06d3.webm?t=1766576446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
